-- AIG shares price at $32.50 in secondary offering
-- 
-- Mon Sep 10, 2012 7:42pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/09/10/us-aig-offering-idUSBRE8891DW20120910

 

 (Reuters) - A secondary offering for American International Group Inc shares by the U.S. Treasury Department was priced at $32.50 per share on Monday evening, according to an underwriting source. 
 The Treasury Department said on Sunday it would sell $18 billion worth of shares in the bailed-out insurer and set aside another $2.7 billion worth of shares to cover overallotments. (Reporting by  Olivia Oran ; Editing by  Gary Hill )